gov.nih.nlm.meme.integrity
Class EnforcableIntegrityVector

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.integrity.IntegrityVector.Default
      gov.nih.nlm.meme.integrity.EnforcableIntegrityVector
All Implemented Interfaces:
IntegrityVector
public class EnforcableIntegrityVector
extends IntegrityVector.Default

Represents a vector used by an application for enforcing IntegrityChecks. It contains methods for applying the various DataConstraint and MergeInhibitor to concepts used by the application.

Author:
MEME Group
